{"tid":1325204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有無人記得2019年香港枝籤","createTime":"2019-07-16T20:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T21:14:49.000Z","uid":168228,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f01019856e75ce75b8c340459aa188cc2712a622","tid":1325204,"uid":168228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T20:34:56.000Z","msg":"石田為業喜非常，畫餅將來未見香；<br />\n怎曉田耕耘不得，那知餅食不充腸<br />\n車公真係好靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4a492664b00b8ae3bc6f781ed0a685cf5d682e","tid":1325204,"uid":168228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T20:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190206/59228844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190206%2F59228844&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=7c21ba52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190206%2F59228844&h=7aac162c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190206/59228844</a><br />\n附上蘋果link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3cf1deab286fa0cfb4cf0da191d45fb34664b6","tid":1325204,"uid":168228,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T20:36:40.000Z","msg":"陳師傅又稱，位處南方的香港今年流年不利，容易受西方「三煞位」影響，易招波瀾。他續解釋，西方除可指歐美國家外，也同時代表林鄭月娥；因為林鄭屬雞，雞在天干地支中為酉，同屬西方，故籤文亦反映上天不滿娥特班子的表現。他忠告林鄭應該「對香港人好啲」，施政上切忌走前特首梁振英的「舊路」，香港才能避過外圍災劫。除政治環境在未來一年繼續凶險外，陳又建議市民減少投資，保本為上，因為籤文同時預視今年經濟情況極差，「股票有股票冧，樓市有樓市冧。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135b7c55358f787e75e6a08967cb823c9c3d016a","tid":1325204,"uid":37136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T20:39:14.000Z","m